{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"69664-uh-oh","title":"Uh-oh","description":"What happens when you get too close to some animals and plants? They use all sorts of tricks to protect themselves from danger. Find out in this hilarious book.","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Aparna  Kapur","Radha Rangarajan"],"illustrators":["Kingshuk Chaudhary"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/69664-uh-oh"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/725074/size3/f5dbe41d34eb61fdb426b974dff0fa24.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/725074/size6/f5dbe41d34eb61fdb426b974dff0fa24.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/113672/size6/abd8263d9e6c6a6cd9610304c21f7f40.jpg","text":"Hullo! I’m very quick!","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/113673/size6/fc910ab38501babc4303a60abe24581b.jpg","text":"Try to press down on my tail.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/113674/size6/39eb05e2f8b739437c9dc00e92896063.jpg","text":"Uh-oh!","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/120643/size6/16eaf7ef6d4ca62538dac37c3dd984d0.jpg","text":"Please don’t touch any of my leaves.\nI am busy looking at the clouds.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/119106/size6/257b37b785feb90083149735b3b5b8de.jpg","text":"Oh no!","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/113677/size6/a4cba391c2d6169a6860d53fd1d49056.jpg","text":"I’m not always this little.\nSee what happens when you yell CABBAGE!","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/113678/size6/2180481e266b8be1d0c48d78cde6cc4f.jpg","text":"Pffft!","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/119108/size6/0c71318dbcd5e190c57b710398be1ee9.jpg","text":"I’m scared of nothing! Not even lions.\nROAAAARRRR as loudly as you can.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/113680/size6/d95d9de4c59031e9398bcfdf0830c3b2.jpg","text":"Tshing!","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/113681/size6/aaa029c9b9c3a3b8abf478e49fb15be1.jpg","text":"An odd thing happens when I hear songs.\nSo do not sing OODLEY OODLEY OOOO to me.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/114329/size6/311565ca867f926988b3e0f3a0dee22a.jpg","text":"Shoop!","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/120366/size6/af07ec6bae080440f4fb5ee4fb56926e.jpg","text":"Oi you, show me your scariest face.\nGo on!","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/120365/size6/490781bf6864803b8ca7eddf884e8de9.jpg","text":"AAAA!","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/113684/size6/3bdd776549473b77c76fd5b059d6135c.jpg","text":"I should remain calm. But I don’t remember why.\nSo no sudden movements, okay?","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/113685/size6/82ab1931d481082535428f6951f35aaa.jpg","text":"Uh-oh!","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/130111/size6/f7f0c83769c3725cbeacd39a92968186.jpg","text":"Meet the Characters\nGecko\nPorcupine\nChameleon\nPangolin\nPufferfish\nOctopus\nTouch-me-not","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":16,"words":108}}